<span>Physicians Choice Dialysis Opens Center in Attalla, Alabama with 100% Deficiency Free Approval by the Alabama State Department of Health and CMS:</span>

	<p>Physicians Choice Dialysis proudly announces the newest addition of its Alabama footprint with the Medicare certification and licensure of Physicians Choice Dialysis of Attalla.  Physicians Choice Dialysis of Attalla offers an array of amenities to the local community including: heated massage chairs, flat screen televisions, WIFI capabilities, and state of the art equipment.  The facility is located in <strong>Attalla, Alabama Etowah County at 801 Gilbert Ferry Road SE, Attalla, AL 35954</strong>. 
    <br><br>
     The new "state of the art" facility features In-Center Hemodialysis and all shifts are available.  These options allow our patient population to select the shift that will best suit their lifestyle as well as medical need.  Partnering with Dr. Kabir, Dr. Kwan and Dr. Hwang in the local area, Physicians Choice Dialysis provides education to the local population relating to renal disease and treatment options allowing patients to customize their treatment regime.  The facility was the fourth facility to open in 13 months in the state of Alabama under Physicians Choice Dialysis management and ownership.  
     <br><br>
     This continued focus on the Alabama market area displays the dedication of Physicians Choice Dialysis to continue to support local areas and affiliate with local nephrologists to accomplish these goals.

